{"tid":2149320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"亂世中，竹君和婉霞為我作深喉檢測","createTime":"2020-08-10T10:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T11:50:48.000Z","uid":120847,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"63e68b6dc4dbe37a75371ea1fa34be8dab97dfce","tid":2149320,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"在這烽煙四起的一年，瘟疫加上中美角力，初出茅廬的我馬不停蹄遊走於各大記者會，24小時為大眾的知情權奔波。<br />\n<br />\n長期的折騰，是對我年輕肉體的挑戰。身很累，心更累。<br />\n<br />\n下午5時，衛生署記者會完結了，連續20小時的工作亦暫告一段落。當我把記者會的筆記發回報館，起身離座時，房間已空無一人。我拖著疲倦的身驅步向門口之際，突然聽到竹君的聲音<br />\n<br />\n竹君: &ldquo;點呀deedee，收得工未呢? 唉我仲要返醫院大把野跟...你好生面口喎，岩岩入行?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;係...咁都俾你睇得出&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n竹君: &ldquo;後生仔唔好捱壞自己...&rdquo; 竹君一邊講，一邊向我走近。嬌小嘅竹君頭頂剛好到我胸膛。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;搵食冇辦法啦。呢行壓力好大......&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n竹君伸手摸住我結實嘅手臂問: &ldquo;咁你平時有冇做運動...你都幾結實喎...嘩...&rdquo; 竹君嘴角微揚，身體開始愈黎愈接近，雙手開始不規矩上下摸著我的手臂。縱使我身驅很疲倦，久違了的男性賀爾蒙卻被激活了。"},{"pid":"b73cae1dd06c0d5ad231671c31abc5323a93209e","tid":2149320,"uid":193125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ae281de867fa19e6c048d957d2fd973b51508b","tid":2149320,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:47:06.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;都有做下gym嘅...&rdquo; 竹君不停摸我手臂，對眼一邊向上稍住我。我雙手都開始失去控制，直接把竹君抱入懷裡。<br />\n<br />\n竹君: &ldquo;黎，訓低，等醫生幫你檢查下&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我同竹君就躺在記者會的長枱上相擁而吻。進擊的舌攻，流露了她抑壓已久的慾望。<br />\n<br />\n竹君: &ldquo;呀...死啦...&rdquo; 伴隨著喘氣聲，她的手開始為我解鈕除衫"},{"pid":"72a6010266d087b22ea773a0be1aaed144314bfd","tid":2149320,"uid":224561,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oy1gQLF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOy1gQLF.gif&h=61c12f24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd6a2afdeab30dedafdf14f3fdcd87fb464a880e","tid":2149320,"uid":67840,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200330/_2020033018502138403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200330%2F_2020033018502138403.jpg&h=17259fcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27c8c4956668a81f6c7ac9ffd80db86c9eacfa62","tid":2149320,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xn7XrA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xn7XrA.gif&h=26ded0d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b098ca7d6b0930a1f15f6952b05b6fd0c522745","tid":2149320,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"慧玲得唔得吖"},{"pid":"b4dca37cf9c0758b31181b034b602fb542d74be8","tid":2149320,"uid":120847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"我和竹君兩個亂世中擁吻的男女，彷彿忘記了世界發生著什麼事。她一手把枱上的米高峰和文件撥到地上，脫下我灰灰殘殘的西褲和皮鞋。從我汗濕的內褲二話不說地抽出大肉棒，喘著氣說:&quot;我要幫你做個深喉檢測&quot;"},{"pid":"756d78f9f447b28bfe23869cf4cf7bd763dd4aec","tid":2149320,"uid":218750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"嘩屌點起機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1edbbd982ece103fa046d569bf366d8425d27d7e","tid":2149320,"uid":359626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">@鈕祜祿&middot;甄嬛</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5020e8e9c8da006bfa39e7e7d2d904afb1032a8","tid":2149320,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef3c4945730ac01d4e9e05a774b5b5e3a197f87","tid":2149320,"uid":2475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:50:48.000Z","msg":"正皮係我比的, 請繼續"}]}